Task : Term Deposit Subscription Prediction (Classification)
Objective: Predict whether a bank customer will subscribe to a term deposit based on marketing campaign data.

Key Skills: Random Forest Classification, Feature Encoding, Explainable AI (XAI) using SHAP.

Technical Challenges Overcome: Managed high-dimensional categorical data and interpreted "black-box" model decisions using SHAP to identify that duration and poutcome were the primary drivers of subscription.

Outcome: Developed a robust classification pipeline that provides both high predictive accuracy and transparency for business stakeholders.
